  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/7487260953a35988b0426f83b5f169e8.webp?t=1764663176\" width=617 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本ゲームはプレイ時間 2時間～3時間程度のノベルゲームです。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一か月後に殺す</strong>死刑囚二人と仲良くしましょう。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >悪役の過去が好きな人にオススメです。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/26b1af2792c9096fa676a3baab050f76.webp?t=1764663176\" width=617 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/ceb2f9d9054bea838b6c1f18e67d01d2.avif?t=1764663176\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras_big/ceb2f9d9054bea838b6c1f18e67d01d2.avif?t=1764663176 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巨大な月に照らされた工業都市ミストブリッジ、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >そこで一つの事件が終結した。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聖職者が破戒の罪を問われ残虐死する連続殺人事件、通称「焼尽問答」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >その犯人である二人の男に死刑判決が下る。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/afbc315077b93f0c06a9098ac5b887a7.avif?t=1764663176\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras_big/afbc315077b93f0c06a9098ac5b887a7.avif?t=1764663176 width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刑務官である貴方は犯人二人の教誨……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >カウンセリングのようなものを任されることになった。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刑死に至る人生。共犯者の奇妙な因縁。信仰と罪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたは死にゆく二人から何を見、何を聞くのか。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反省の色を見せない二人に、罪を教えることはできるのか。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >彼らの死に、よい後悔のあらんことを。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/f253c6eb7085490dd3c414b624bc6a4c.webp?t=1764663176\" width=617 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/d0d2306c8a562b113ff45b3247966898.avif?t=1764663176\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >毎日の面会を通じて物語が進行するほか、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与えられた時間を消費することで死刑囚と雑談したり、事件にまつわる書類を読んだりすることができる。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事件の詳細を聞くも良し、雑談するもよし。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >話題の種類は30種以上！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/a2755da76fd53f748a1e5803606b0caf.avif?t=1764663176\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras_big/a2755da76fd53f748a1e5803606b0caf.avif?t=1764663176 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ここでの選択が思わぬ結末につながることも。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/628d4b6ae57b3e6cd35f994be3e997ce.avif?t=1764663176\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >また、本編で登場した単語は辞書機能で見返すことができる。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/d4de985d8f870bdd67ef9294e4d88e74.webp?t=1764663176\" width=617 height=36 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/a2d7cf895045d05401aa1a5dffc1a3bf.avif?t=1764663176\" width=614 height=252 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>004番　パニ</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >残忍な殺人犯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事件では主に実行を担当していた。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >軽い記憶喪失があり、過去の出来事がおぼつかない。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/cf87ad451e81eb13db85c252a66dd3ea.avif?t=1764663176\" width=614 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>888番　ギル</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狡猾な教唆犯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事件では主に計画、工作を担当していた。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宗教的な名家の出身で神聖な血を持つ。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461460/extras/3b5dfaf1f90e6dc4f33d23938bd225b8.webp?t=1764663176\" width=617 height=36 /></span>二次創作について</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基本的に愛があれば自由です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >エロ、グロ、非公式カップリング描写は適切なゾーニングを行ってください。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >配信、実況について</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >バッドエンドスチル、23日以降の画面をサムネイルに使用しないでください。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >それ以外はご自由にどうぞ。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
